<p>Real estate company registration in Gurugram is a two-tier process - MCA incorporation under the Companies Act, 2013 stacked with HARERA Gurugram project registration under Section 4 of the RERA Act, 2016. The risk of doing this without specialist help is not the filing fee.</p>
